    {
      "id": "edge-A-pattern2-dns-dnf-dq",
      "description": "A版 パターン2: DNS/DNF/DQは進出対象外とし、残る完漕艇だけで繰り上げる",
      "template": "alljapan-2026-A",
      "pattern": 2,
      "input": {
        "entries_count": 12,
        "heat_results": {
          "H1": [
            { "crew_id": "crew_A", "time_ms": 200000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_C", "time_ms": 210000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_E", "time_ms": 220000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_G", "time_ms": 230000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_I", "time_ms": 240000, "status": "dnf" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_K", "time_ms": null, "status": "dns" }
          ],
          "H2": [
            { "crew_id": "crew_B", "time_ms": 205000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_D", "time_ms": 215000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_F", "time_ms": 225000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_H", "time_ms": 235000, "status": "finish" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_J", "time_ms": 245000, "status": "dq" },
            { "crew_id": "crew_L", "time_ms": 250000, "status": "finish" }
          ]
        }
      },
      "expected": {
        "classification_notes": [
          "SPEC_engine.md §5.1 step3 / §6 / §5.2 からの手計算。実装出力の転記ではない。",
          "1. 各組 status==='finish' のみ着順対象: H1完漕=A(1),C(2),E(3),G(4) [I:dnf/K:dns除外] / H2完漕=B(1),D(2),F(3),H(4),L(5) [J:dq除外]",
          "2. protected rank={1}。1着をタイム順に並べ A(200000)<B(205000) → 1.1.H=crew_A, 2.1.H=crew_B ※この `N.M.H` 解釈（N=1着群のタイム順位／M=着順）はテンプレートとエンジンの実装semanticsであり、SPEC §3.1の記述（N=着順/M=組番号）とは食い違う。SPEC側の記述誤りとして要修正（本テストの進出可否には影響せず）",
          "3. 残る完漕艇をタイム昇順でHT付番: C(210000)=1.HT, D(215000)=2.HT, E(220000)=3.HT, F(225000)=4.HT, G(230000)=5.HT, H(235000)=6.HT, L(250000)=7.HT",
          "4. tail枠=全12行-protected2枠=10。完漕tailは7艇のため 8.HT/9.HT/10.HT は占有者なし（§6『対象外艇を除外した後に上からN艇を取る』）",
